.\" Manpage for note.
.TH man 1 "20 Feb 2022" "1.0" "note man page"
.SH NAME
note \- Simple notes manager
.SH SYNOPSIS
note
note COMMAND [NOTE]
.SH DESCRIPTION
CLI Notes manager

.SH COMMANDS
.PP
\fBinit\fR
.RS 4
Creates dirs ~/.notes and initialize git repository
.RE
.PP
\fBedit (note)\fR
.RS 4
Creates or edit existing note with $EDITOR, after save changes
.RE
.PP
\fBshow (note)\fR
.RS 4
Render note in terminal by glow
.RE
.PP
\fBrender (note)\fR
.RS 4
Render note in browser by grip on localhost:6751
.RE
.PP
\fBmv (note) (new-note-name)\fR
.RS 4
Rename note
.RE
.PP
\fBrm (note)\fR
.RS 4
Deletes note and commits
.RE
.PP
.SH OPTIONAL DEPENDENCIES
python-grip, glow
.SH AUTHOR
Kan (thek4n@yandex.ru)
https://github.com/thek4n
